            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Reboil a kettle</p><p>While the steak is cooking, peel and finely slice your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Once the steak is cooked, transfer to a plate to rest, reserve the pan</p><p>Dissolve your <strong>pho broth base </strong>and <strong>beef stock mix</strong> in 600ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [750ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[900ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>pho stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1688736782041-x200.jpg",
