            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the onion is softening, cut your <strong>lime[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Top, tail, peel and chop your <strong>carrot[s]</strong> into matchsticks</p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> roughly, including the stalks</p><p>Strip your <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems, discard the stems</p><p>Slice your<strong> red chilli[es]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>finely</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1688736787888-x200.jpg",
