          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1688736792949-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>pho</strong> in bowls topped with the <strong>sliced steak</strong>, <strong>carrot matchsticks</strong>, <strong>chilli rounds </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!), <strong>chopped coriander </strong>and<strong> mint leaves</strong></p><p>Garnish with a<strong> lime wedge </strong>– this is your <strong>fiery Vietnamese-style steak pho</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
